snippet.title: Urban Flow - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Urban Flow is now available on Nintendo Switch!

Manage the city lights and try to avoid the chaos! Immerse yourself in a beautiful, hand-crafted, low-poly world to discover the enormous satisfaction of watching the hundreds of tiny, colorful cars flowing through the streets – all while listening to the chill, urban music.

Play by yourself or with friends in scalable drop-in, drop-out local co-op mode for two, three, or four players!

Become one with the flow. The Urban Flow!

Available now! https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/urban-flow-switch/

#UrbanFlowGame #NintendoSwitch
